OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fbright evening with a few light
OL,7,Fshowers. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee further light showers between
OL,9,Fclear spells. Remaining breezy on
OL,10,Fnorthern coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRather cloudy in the northeast
OL,13,Fwith a few showers. Drier and brighter
OL,14,Fin the southwest with the best of
OL,15,Fsunnier spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
